完就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果送房比我嗰日同女朋友黎就會周圍遊</blockquote><br />\n你好叻叻 我識十個過澳門的九個半都係黎沖涼同賭兩口的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97fd1be09dabf0d9b2e3576692d82db82c0fda5","tid":540280,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0425989aea9977bfa44f2ce7a77b33fa4db9454","tid":540280,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85d03f6f16aa7470a035deb7e50e1de402dc7dc3","tid":540280,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a78bfaa546cc3356c7d877b710ff5c39ce9e50ae","tid":540280,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T10:41:06.000Z","msg":"D雞model既樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T10:43:11.000Z","msg":"好貴 北姑model 3k"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T10:43:57.000Z","msg":"唔使"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T12:04:30.000Z","msg":"留名跟蓋sir學叫雞"},{"pid":"44c8ee41ea4f1e3f07d4058124b5b222341c266c","tid":540280,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T12:05:01.000Z","msg":"我唔叫雞"},{"pid":"aa716145c6e704197cca8fd20e0d3fc6905c1f10","tid":540280,"uid":12328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T12:07:22.000Z","msg":"兩千洗費達成。閃"},{"pid":"cef7caf778ebf3eb09cbb43b333c6bdc1c162fa1","tid":540280,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa716145c6e704197cca8fd20e0d3fc6905c1f10","tid":540280,"uid":12328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T12:07:22.000Z","msg":"兩千洗費達成。閃"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T12:08:47.000Z","msg":"連續十幾日贏錢好易 但一輸就通常會加注十幾倍 一日輸返落去。<br />\n<br />\n我一年前,起威記一晚贏左二十四萬,跟住連果二萬本都輸埋,第二日再賣曬股票,攞左12萬去,最後清袋。<br />\n<br />\n輸到袋剩下五百。<br />\n<br />\n5萬出發，輸左1萬已想停，再輸多5千老虎機。<br />\n<br />\n卒之三日,就係三日,戶口四十五萬積蓄冇晒。<br />\n<br />\n最後五舊走去買閒對，差啲唔夠船飛錢。<br />\n<br />\n賭左都冇一年，輸左成40 個。就係皆因win $ 起。爭成十幾萬數。<br />\n<br />\n人始終唔可以十成理智，魔鬼總有方法迫您動火。<br />\n<br />\n直線插水後 宜家借緊ua定期加循環共三萬蚊。"},{"pid":"10eb89b75